name = "Bad Habits"
difficulty = "Easy"
description = "A while ago, I visited the Doctor in that abandoned school nearby. He told me that I should cut out all my \"bad habits,\" but the old fucker smokes himself, so screw him!

You're probably just one of those modern-day hippies who only licks mint pastilles when things get rough, but if you happen to find one of these, bring a pack or two and some matches as well."
